refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
arraystream_get_meta_data resourcestream
Returns information about an existing stream.

&reftitle.parameters;
stream
The stream can be any stream created by fopen, fsockopen and pfsockopen.

&reftitle.examples;
stream_get_meta_data example
<?php $url = 'http://www.example.com/';
if (!$fp = fopen($url, 'r')) { trigger_error("Unable to open URL ($url)", E_USER_ERROR); }
$meta = stream_get_meta_data($fp);
print_r($meta);
fclose($fp); ?>
